I mean, how many of these can we watch? It’s usually the same old story with the same plot line. Difference now is that the characters are going to get lamer and the CGI is getting worse. I mean, it’s like watching cartoons at this point. I wish people would stop eating this stuff up and start hungering for some real cinema where the film isn’t heavily reliant on special effects. I want to see real movies, starting real people. No thanks on Natalie Portman as Thor and who cares about Black widow and Black Panther? Stop paying for this doodoo.
